detail_desc: Calf-length dress in embroidered mesh with a smocked, frilled collar and opening with buttons at the back of the neck. Long raglan sleeves with wide, smocked cuffs and a smocked seam with a frill trim at the waist. V-neck underdress in airy jersey with adjustable spaghetti shoulder straps.
Cold shoulder, knee-length dress in mesh with embroidery. Wide shoulder straps, a wide flounce at the top, a seam at the waist and a gently flared skirt in a double layer of mesh. Lined.

Playsuit in an airy plumeti weave with sequins and beaded embroidery at the front. V-neck with a sewn-in wrapover and concealed press-stud at the neckline, and an opening with a button at the back of the neck. Elasticated seam and detachable, twisted ties with tassels at the waist. Lace trim around the neckline, cuffs and hems. Jersey lining.
Short dress in sequined mesh with a V-neck and wrapover top. Long, slightly wider sleeves with elastication at the cuffs, and an elasticated seam and satin ribbon at the waist. Jersey lining.
Fitted, off-the-shoulder top in soft cotton jersey with short sleeves.
